column2: PDF books provide a more enjoyable reading experience compared to Hardcover books.
column3: It is easier to focus and retain information when reading from a Digital book compared to a physical book.
column4: It is more convenient to carry a hardcover book when travelling.
column5: There are significant environmental impacts from producing and shipping hardcover books.
column6: The sentimental attachment that comes with owning physical books are more valuable than PDFs.
column7: It is more effective to study from a hardcover textbook than from a PDF.
